            <field name="strengths">Thorough preparation approach, excellent attention to detail, proactive backup planning.</field>
            <field name="improvement_areas">Earlier testing of technical setups, more time allocated for rehearsal.</field>
            <field name="recommendations">1. Test demo environments 24 hours before presentations, 2. Schedule practice sessions with colleagues, 3. Create standard presentation checklists.</field>
